{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "29327184-1379-472a-9176-949b02b46192", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/29327184-1379-472a-9176-949b02b46192@1.pkg/1772597711730/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597712117", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/29327184-1379-472a-9176-949b02b46192@1.pkg/1772597711730/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597712117"}, "identifier": "29327184-1379-472a-9176-949b02b46192", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p align=\"justify\">本题考查提高防护能力。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p align=\"justify\">①④：根据所学，在传染病多发的季节，要戴好口罩、勤洗手，做好个人防护；在危险来临时，我们要保持头脑冷静，就近、快速逃离到安全地带。据此，遭遇火灾，用打湿毛巾捂着口鼻，有序逃离，故①④说法正确；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">②：雷雨天气到大树下避雨，容易遭遇雷击发生意外，故②说法错误；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">③：发现有人落水时，应在保证自身安全的前提下进行施救或者向他人求救，不能贸然下水救人，故③说法错误；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">故本题选B。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">（改编）每个人都是自己生命安全的第一责任人，日常生活中，我们需要掌握科学自救和救他的技巧和方法。以下正确的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">①在传染病多发的季节，要戴好口罩、勤洗手</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">②遇到暴雨、打雷天气，应及时到大树下避雨</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">③发现有人溺水时，义无反顾，直接下水救人&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>④遭遇火灾，用打湿毛巾捂着口鼻，有序逃离&nbsp;</p>\n", "title": "（改编）每个人都是自己生命安全的第一责任人，日常生活中，我们需要掌握科学自救和救他的技巧和方法。以下正确的是（   ）①在传染病多发的季节，要戴好口罩、勤洗手②遇到暴雨、打雷天气，应及时到大树下避雨③发现有人溺水时，义无反顾，直接下水救人    ④遭遇火灾，用打湿毛巾捂着口鼻，有序逃离 ", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/29327184-1379-472a-9176-949b02b46192@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754969312098", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>②④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\n\t<li>③④</li>\n</ol>\n"}], "prompt": "<p style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">（改编）每个人都是自己生命安全的第一责任人，日常生活中，我们需要掌握科学自救和救他的技巧和方法。以下正确的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">①在传染病多发的季节，要戴好口罩、勤洗手</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">②遇到暴雨、打雷天气，应及时到大树下避雨</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">③发现有人溺水时，义无反顾，直接下水救人&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>④遭遇火灾，用打湿毛巾捂着口鼻，有序逃离&nbsp;</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-